               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Sǝnkǝssār ”Synaxarion” for the second half of the year (fols.
                     4ra-219vc)&#xD; I-1) Maggābit (fols. 4ra-35vc)&#xD; I-2) Miyāzyā (fols.
                     36ra-62vc) &#xD; I-3) Gǝnbot (fols. 63ra-96vc) &#xD; I-4) Sane (fols.
                     97ra-131vb)&#xD; I-5) Ḥamle (fols. 132ra-178vc)&#xD; I-6) Naḥāse (fols.
                     179ra-213vb)&#xD; I-7) Ṗagʷǝmen (fols. 213vb-219vc)&#xD; The commemorative
                     notices are followed by ʿarke-hymns&#xD; &#xD; Additiones 1-2;
                     colophon.</summary>
